abstract: List of 48 of 49 victims killed in Orlando, Fla, nightclub massacre identified by city.
snippet: The authorities have identified all but one of the 49 victims killed in Sunday’s massacre at the Pulse nightclub in Orlando, Fla. They ranged in age from 18 to 50.
